{
  "stem": "748.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When you don't agree what the professor say, it-- it-- it has to be this book you have to study.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You don't win nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Before we continue with Benny, can we come back to what-- after the war, you were in Bergen-Belsen with your husband?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think, two years.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- we-- when Benny was born, we went to Sweden, to Malmo.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's a-- it's beautiful people and a beautiful-- a beautiful country.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know now.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We are, I think, 45 years in-- in-- in Toronto already.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Leninberg, in Germany.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I was a witness, like you-- you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There is all papers, what I talk in court.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "35 Germans.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was-- there was 34 SS men in--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, in Nuremberg.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A Jewish [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Mayor. ?] You can imagine.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when I-- when they call me in, if I know this SS man, then I fainted.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then, he came-- he was a doctor, too-- and they-- they-- they-- I don't know-- they took me to the nursery there by the-- by the court.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was two days lying there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nurses, doctors, was with me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When I felt better, then I come back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Mayor ?] says to me-- he came-- he says, what is your name, dear?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I says, Sarah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] You still remember your Jewish name?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I says, sure.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Then he says to me, Jewish, in the ear, [SPEAKING YIDDISH].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They will be hanged.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And there, SS man, what came in the crematorium and take me out, he says, when I take you out from crematorium, why you make me to die?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I says, a simple thing-- because you did the same thing to our people.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
